http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two most decorated athletes in the Games' history, Michael Phelps and Martin Fourcade, unveiled the gold, silver, and bronze medals.\", \"from\": 5093, \"to\": 5229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5148, \"end\": 5162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.521157016416371e-41, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}, {\"begin\": 5167, \"end\": 5182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Fourcade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Martin Fourcade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Fourcade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Fourcade\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At one point, there was a live crossover to the early morning welcome ceremony at the surfing venue, 16,000 km away in the Pacific island of Tahiti.\", \"from\": 5231, \"to\": 5379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5372, \"end\": 5378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999988195165916, \"rank\": 1.1804851904502474e-06, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since the last Games - the Winter Olympics held in Beijing in 2022 - wars have erupted in Ukraine and Gaza, providing a tense international backdrop.\", \"from\": 5381, \"to\": 5530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5432, \"end\": 5439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997393861619172, \"rank\": 0.0002606817751826562, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 5471, \"end\": 5478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999985004590018, \"rank\": 1.0093534320666648e-06, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 5483, \"end\": 5487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"score\": 0.7895642757973069, \"rank\": 0.26652133417545576, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France is at its highest level of security, though officials have repeatedly said there is no specific threat to the opening ceremony or the Games.\", \"from\": 5531, \"to\": 5678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5531, \"end\": 5537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5012365867739817e-13, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Israeli competitors are being escorted by elite tactical units to and from events and given 24-hour protection throughout the Olympics due to the war in Gaza, officials say.\", \"from\": 5680, \"to\": 5853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5680, \"end\": 5687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"score\": 0.9596573186530979, \"rank\": 0.02774551310078763, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\"}, {\"begin\": 5833, \"end\": 5837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"score\": 0.7895642757973069, \"rank\": 0.26652133417545576, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Israel delegation got some boos, but also a lot of cheers, as it sailed by spectators, Reuters reporters saw.\", \"from\": 5855, \"to\": 5968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5859, \"end\": 5865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6389449629382132e-14, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 5946, \"end\": 5953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.76964058756484e-23, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chants of \\\"Palestine!\", \"from\": 5969, \"to\": 5990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Palestine!\", \"from\": 5991, \"to\": 6001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5991, \"end\": 6000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9942350606525473, \"rank\": 0.005774285180717005, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Palestine!\\\"\", \"from\": 6002, \"to\": 6013, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6002, \"end\": 6011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9942350606525473, \"rank\": 0.005774285180717005, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"rose from the crowd as the boat passed.\", \"from\": 6014, \"to\": 6053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Macron, who won a second mandate two years ago, had hoped the Olympics would cement his legacy.\", \"from\": 6055, \"to\": 6150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6055, \"end\": 6061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0195603110871342e-16, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But his failed bet on a snap legislative election has weakened him and cast a shadow over his moment on the international stage.\", \"from\": 6151, \"to\": 6279, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 6281, \"to\": 6324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 6326, \"to\": 6335, \"entities\": []}]}"